dct_title_s: Geōtechnikos chartēs tēs Helladas = Engineering geological map of Greece / Engineering Geology Department (IGME) ; compilation of the engineering geological map: B. Andronopoulos ; I. Theodossiou-Drandaki ; [and others].
dct_description_sm: Relief shown by contours and spot heights. Includes 2 inset maps: Map of landsliding urban areas of the Greek territory / by A. Eleftheriou ; Map of mean precipitation.
dct_publisher_sm: Athēnai : Institute of Geology and Mineral Exploration, 1993.
